WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 11=

01:47.550 --> 01:48.580
Did you have a dream?

01:50.420 --> 01:51.260
A dream?

01:51.990 --> 01:53.580
You mean the kind mortals have?

01:56.110 --> 01:57.060
What are you doing here?

02:00.270 --> 02:01.110
When I woke up,

02:02.500 --> 02:03.700
I couldn't feel my body.

02:04.420 --> 02:05.470
I thought I was dead.

02:06.550 --> 02:07.940
I couldn't sleep, so I came by.

02:10.180 --> 02:11.070
It seems you

02:11.900 --> 02:13.020
had a pleasant dream.

02:15.670 --> 02:16.830
You dreamed of your parents.

02:19.070 --> 02:20.140
Were you missing home?

02:25.180 --> 02:26.350
I dreamed

02:29.550 --> 02:30.900
they taught me dining manners.

02:31.860 --> 02:32.860
What dining manners?

02:34.350 --> 02:35.420
Like Chenying's father.

02:36.110 --> 02:37.300
I took his obsession,

02:37.700 --> 02:38.830
so I'd look after Chenying

02:38.890 --> 02:39.790
and then entrust him

02:39.790 --> 02:40.670
to a decent family.

02:41.110 --> 02:42.270
That is the deal.

02:44.350 --> 02:45.683
Is it the rule of the Spirit World

02:46.390 --> 02:47.580
to make a deal

02:47.950 --> 02:49.150
before taking one's obsession?

02:49.510 --> 02:50.350
No.

02:51.510 --> 02:52.460
It's my rule.

02:53.790 --> 02:54.630
Why?

02:56.580 --> 02:57.753
As the Sovereign of Spirits,

02:58.420 --> 03:00.070
why do you use an exchange

03:01.350 --> 03:02.670
to grant mortals their wishes?

03:04.670 --> 03:05.510
Why?

03:07.860 --> 03:09.110
There aren't so many reasons

03:09.110 --> 03:10.070
in this world?

03:10.550 --> 03:11.740
I just want to, okay?

03:20.420 --> 03:21.580
Your parents

03:22.790 --> 03:24.140
must both be very gentle,

03:28.830 --> 03:29.740
just like you.

03:32.070 --> 03:32.910
Gentle?

03:37.300 --> 03:38.460
You can't taste flavors.

03:39.140 --> 03:40.453
Yet you can make sugar figurines.

03:41.740 --> 03:42.830
You can't see colors,

03:43.790 --> 03:45.300
yet you paint masterfully.

03:47.110 --> 03:48.180
You can't hear the tune,

03:49.550 --> 03:50.700
yet you can play instruments.

03:53.580 --> 03:54.790
You can't even sense

03:54.790 --> 03:55.640
such ordinary things

03:55.660 --> 03:56.680
as breathing or dreaming.

03:57.990 --> 03:59.180
Why learn these skills

03:59.350 --> 04:00.200
that even mortals

04:00.200 --> 04:01.070
find hard to master?

04:02.140 --> 04:03.550
Surely, your parents

04:05.830 --> 04:07.230
hoped that through these,

04:08.670 --> 04:10.140
you could feel this world.

04:18.420 --> 04:19.260
Perhaps.

04:21.150 --> 04:21.990
They...

04:25.060 --> 04:25.900
have passed away?

04:29.860 --> 04:30.700
My mother

04:32.260 --> 04:33.990
passed naturally with age.

04:36.910 --> 04:37.750
As for my father...

04:39.670 --> 04:40.790
I heard it was for love.

04:47.790 --> 04:49.590
So, with five senses, I can dream.

04:52.060 --> 04:53.670
I dream mortal dreams now.

04:56.190 --> 04:57.139
Everything in the dream

04:57.150 --> 04:58.060
felt so very real.

04:59.660 --> 05:00.500
I'd already forgotten

05:00.500 --> 05:01.740
that they were gone.

05:03.300 --> 05:04.150
I could even

05:07.990 --> 05:08.940
still feel

05:08.940 --> 05:09.860
their warmth.

05:22.620 --> 05:23.460
Wake up.

05:25.590 --> 05:26.740
The dream is over.

05:32.110 --> 05:33.590
If I still had spirit power,

05:34.110 --> 05:35.500
your hand would be gone by now.

05:40.260 --> 05:41.740
So, luck favors me after all.

05:42.300 --> 05:43.470
I got to keep this hand.

05:47.740 --> 05:48.580
(His hand)

05:50.150 --> 05:51.420
(is soft and warm.)

06:26.550 --> 06:27.910
I don't need mortal food.

06:30.300 --> 06:31.470
You're in a mortal body now.

06:32.550 --> 06:33.790
You use up strength every day.

06:34.710 --> 06:35.550
Food does more

06:35.820 --> 06:36.990
than fill the stomach.

06:38.230 --> 06:39.820
At times, it brings new sensations.

06:41.300 --> 06:42.230
Please give it a try.

06:49.550 --> 06:50.740
This is tofu.

06:53.420 --> 06:55.590
Tofu is soft and silky.

06:55.790 --> 06:57.030
You have to hold it like this.

06:57.110 --> 06:57.960
Have a taste.

07:10.150 --> 07:11.420
The texture of tofu

07:12.350 --> 07:13.790
is as smooth as a jade bangle

07:15.500 --> 07:16.820
and as soft and slick as mud.

07:18.230 --> 07:19.230
You can try this one too.

07:20.230 --> 07:21.180
This one is crisp.

07:22.500 --> 07:23.550
This is delicate and dense.

07:42.180 --> 07:43.030
Try this.

07:44.110 --> 07:44.950
And this as well.

07:59.260 --> 08:00.100
What is your name?

08:02.460 --> 08:03.300
Hey,

08:03.300 --> 08:04.140
come and eat.

08:05.710 --> 08:06.620
Xiaoxiao,

08:06.620 --> 08:07.470
don't you like it?

08:13.260 --> 08:14.670
Since you have no kin,

08:15.420 --> 08:16.740
I'll look after you for a while

08:18.260 --> 08:19.500
and then entrust you

08:19.500 --> 08:20.790
to a good family.

08:24.150 --> 08:24.990
Finished crying?

08:25.710 --> 08:26.550
Go bury your father.

08:37.540 --> 08:38.900
You've just been out for a day.

08:39.430 --> 08:40.310
If you catch a chill,

08:40.310 --> 08:41.323
I don't want to tend you.

08:43.380 --> 08:44.380
Xiaoxiao,

08:44.380 --> 08:46.110
you won't cast me aside, will you?

08:46.990 --> 08:47.900
Nonsense.

08:48.830 --> 08:50.310
I'm your only family now.

08:50.310 --> 08:51.590
How could I cast you aside?

08:52.070 --> 08:54.430
You scared me.

08:57.830 --> 08:59.430
Xiaoxiao,

09:00.190 --> 09:01.780
I won't throw a tantrum again.

09:03.260 --> 09:05.430
Just let me stay by your side.

09:35.860 --> 09:36.740
Xiaoxiao,

09:36.740 --> 09:37.580
I...

09:40.110 --> 09:40.950
Hi, Chenying.

09:41.470 --> 09:42.310
Come and eat.

09:46.140 --> 09:46.980
Come on.

09:49.260 --> 09:50.710
Xiaoxiao has eaten plenty.

09:51.470 --> 09:52.310
You should eat too.

09:55.470 --> 09:56.590
Xiaoxiao, you...

09:57.620 --> 09:59.590
You hardly eat much.

09:59.900 --> 10:02.070
Why so much today?

10:03.380 --> 10:04.540
Usually,

10:05.070 --> 10:06.070
food is scarce,

10:06.260 --> 10:07.260
so I leave it for you.

10:07.740 --> 10:09.110
This time, the General is treating,

10:09.620 --> 10:11.140
so of course, I'll eat more.

10:18.230 --> 10:19.110
Is it too hard?

10:20.900 --> 10:21.990
General.

10:24.020 --> 10:25.606
- Xiaoxiao.
- That's not how to eat it.

10:25.950 --> 10:26.790
Don't use your hands.

10:27.430 --> 10:28.270
Here.

10:34.830 --> 10:35.670
Open your mouth.

10:40.990 --> 10:41.830
That's it.

10:47.540 --> 10:48.380
(How can Xiaoxiao)

10:48.380 --> 10:50.260
(eat so much?)

10:51.350 --> 10:52.500
(How strange.)

10:58.260 --> 10:59.100
Simu,

11:00.020 --> 11:01.260
I prepared a gift for you.

11:02.380 --> 11:03.950
I do not need gifts.

11:05.540 --> 11:06.590
- I said…
- Take it

11:06.590 --> 11:07.863
as my apology for the offenses.

11:14.900 --> 11:15.740
Wait a moment.

11:20.490 --> 11:24.140
♪Spring comes; ice and snow thaw♪

11:26.060 --> 11:31.890
♪All things wake, with the east wind♪

11:35.070 --> 11:39.600
♪In the season at its fullest♪

11:42.290 --> 11:43.140
I've noticed

11:43.140 --> 11:44.590
you like soft and furry things.

11:45.590 --> 11:46.430
This is fur

11:46.430 --> 11:47.350
from a white fox

11:47.350 --> 11:48.316
I hunted two years ago.

11:48.960 --> 11:49.800
I didn't know

11:49.800 --> 11:50.900
what I should make of it.

11:51.710 --> 11:53.350
Now, I'm giving it to you as a charm.

11:54.260 --> 11:55.710
That should be its finest usage.

11:58.230 --> 11:59.070
Well?

12:01.230 --> 12:02.070
Do you like it?

12:04.030 --> 12:07.170
♪Let me love with all my heart♪

12:07.310 --> 12:08.150
It's okay.

12:08.150 --> 12:10.860
♪In youthful grace♪

12:11.310 --> 12:14.880
♪With light, carefree words♪

12:14.880 --> 12:17.240
♪Still shining bright♪

12:17.240 --> 12:18.860
Since you had time for such trinkets,

12:19.590 --> 12:20.590
I think Marshal Qin

12:20.590 --> 12:21.590
must be prepared

12:21.590 --> 12:22.470
to strike Youzhou.

12:22.900 --> 12:24.260
If your plan succeeds,

12:24.620 --> 12:26.660
and North Chong is forced
to sign a peace,

12:27.230 --> 12:28.070
your plan

12:28.260 --> 12:30.070
to reclaim

12:30.340 --> 12:31.190
the 17 Prefectures

12:31.190 --> 12:32.380
may never come true.

12:33.470 --> 12:34.350
I'm glad

12:35.860 --> 12:36.740
you care about me.

12:50.620 --> 12:52.060
(Shuozhou)

12:55.740 --> 12:56.580
So lively.

13:18.310 --> 13:19.230
Xiaoxiao.

13:19.270 --> 13:20.140
Xiaoxiao.

13:20.430 --> 13:21.590
Xiaoxiao, where are you going?

13:22.310 --> 13:23.393
The General said

13:23.404 --> 13:24.860
people are having the Rite of Spring.

13:24.860 --> 13:25.700
I want to go see it.

13:28.310 --> 13:29.310
Xiaoxiao,

13:29.830 --> 13:30.830
weren't you once

13:31.140 --> 13:32.900
too lazy to even move?

13:33.540 --> 13:34.430
Why do you

13:34.430 --> 13:36.070
go out strolling every day now?

13:37.350 --> 13:39.430
I have money, so I love shopping.

13:39.950 --> 13:40.790
Xiaoxiao.

13:42.780 --> 13:43.710
Well,

13:44.780 --> 13:46.230
why not take me with you?

14:01.230 --> 14:02.710
Sure. Let's go.

14:09.070 --> 14:10.310
(Xiaoxiao used to dislike)

14:10.310 --> 14:11.830
(joining in on lively events.)

14:14.500 --> 14:16.190
(Forget it.
I'll have fun with Xiaoxiao.)

14:26.350 --> 14:27.190
The Spring Ox!

14:28.350 --> 14:29.700
- My shoe.
- The Spring Ox!

14:30.260 --> 14:31.700
Make way, make way.

14:32.020 --> 14:33.140
- Thanks.
- Slow down.

14:33.140 --> 14:33.980
Slow down.

14:34.540 --> 14:35.500
Xiaoxiao!

14:36.310 --> 14:37.380
Xiaoxiao!

14:38.230 --> 14:39.310
Xiaoxiao!

14:53.620 --> 14:54.860
What a beautiful Spring Ox.

14:54.860 --> 14:56.660
Yes, the General

14:56.660 --> 14:57.590
had people prepare it.

14:57.869 --> 14:58.830
Prepared by the General?

14:58.830 --> 15:00.140
The General had it made.

15:01.430 --> 15:02.270
It's huge.

15:02.590 --> 15:03.540
This ox is really huge.

15:03.540 --> 15:04.380
So huge.

15:17.230 --> 15:18.110
Xiaoxiao!

15:18.310 --> 15:19.150
Xiaoxiao!

15:44.070 --> 15:44.910
Xiaoxiao!

15:47.230 --> 15:48.070
Xiaoxiao!

15:56.860 --> 15:57.700
Xiaoxiao!

16:20.020 --> 16:20.900
Chenying.

16:22.090 --> 16:22.950
Chenying!

16:22.950 --> 16:23.790
Who are you?

16:24.780 --> 16:25.710
Chenying.

16:26.500 --> 16:27.350
Who are you?

16:27.710 --> 16:29.190
Who I am isn't important.

16:29.600 --> 16:30.470
What is important is

16:30.470 --> 16:32.620
who the He Xiaoxiao beside you is.

16:33.350 --> 16:34.260
Xiaoxiao

16:34.260 --> 16:35.380
is just Xiaoxiao.

16:35.590 --> 16:36.860
Clever child.

16:37.430 --> 16:39.140
You already saw through it.

16:39.310 --> 16:41.110
Why deceive yourself?

16:41.350 --> 16:42.470
I'm not.

16:42.860 --> 16:44.540
She is fake.

16:44.710 --> 16:45.550
No.

16:45.830 --> 16:46.950
She is fake.

16:46.950 --> 16:47.790
No.

16:48.350 --> 16:49.350
Fake.

16:49.990 --> 16:51.310
- Fake.
- No.

16:51.780 --> 16:52.990
- She's fake.
- No.

16:53.140 --> 16:53.980
Fake.

16:54.260 --> 16:55.140
Fake!

16:56.020 --> 16:57.070
She's fake.

16:57.070 --> 16:57.910
No.

16:58.070 --> 16:59.540
She's fake.

17:15.710 --> 17:20.150
First whip for favorable weather
and abundant rain.

17:20.390 --> 17:22.260
Good.

17:24.340 --> 17:28.230
Second whip for fertile land
and warm soil.

17:28.430 --> 17:29.340
Good.

17:29.710 --> 17:32.540
Third whip for prosperity.

17:32.540 --> 17:34.060
Good.

17:34.990 --> 17:37.950
Fourth whip for peace
through the four seasons.

17:38.150 --> 17:39.540
Good.

17:40.910 --> 17:44.540
Fifth whip for a bountiful harvest.

17:44.590 --> 17:45.470
Good.

17:45.470 --> 17:49.630
Sixth whip for spring blessings.

17:49.630 --> 17:51.670
Good.

17:53.390 --> 17:54.340
Next,

17:54.340 --> 17:57.060
let us all join in whipping
the Spring Ox.

17:57.230 --> 17:58.630
- Good.
- Good.

17:58.910 --> 17:59.820
The first

18:00.300 --> 18:02.470
to whip the grain

18:02.470 --> 18:03.820
from its belly

18:04.060 --> 18:07.300
wins this little Spring Ox.

18:07.430 --> 18:09.630
- Good.
- Good.

18:11.740 --> 18:12.580
Give me one.

18:30.670 --> 18:32.340
Walk the ox around;

18:32.820 --> 18:34.910
wealth and grain fill the home.

18:35.710 --> 18:37.670
Crack the whip three times;

18:38.020 --> 18:40.260
grain stacks reach the rafters.

18:40.710 --> 18:41.670
Touch the Spring Ox…

18:41.670 --> 18:42.630
Help!

18:43.630 --> 18:44.780
Xiaoxiao!

18:45.710 --> 18:46.630
Help!

18:49.150 --> 18:49.990
Wait!

18:50.390 --> 18:51.230
Stop.

18:51.230 --> 18:52.070
Stop right there.

18:52.300 --> 18:54.300
Stab!

18:55.710 --> 18:57.820
Who is this? Who is he?

18:58.260 --> 18:59.500
I was passing by.

19:00.150 --> 19:02.150
I sensed an evil spirit here.

19:02.950 --> 19:04.710
It's inside this clay ox.

19:05.260 --> 19:06.230
Who exactly are you?

19:11.430 --> 19:12.270
Stab!

19:21.150 --> 19:22.500
Chenying, Chenying?

19:23.130 --> 19:23.990
Chenying?

19:23.990 --> 19:24.910
Everyone.

19:24.910 --> 19:26.710
- Chenying?
- Save yourself.

19:26.910 --> 19:28.420
- Chenying?
- Run!

19:28.430 --> 19:29.470
There's an evil spirit!

19:30.390 --> 19:31.430
How could there be

19:31.430 --> 19:32.630
an evil spirit today?

19:36.390 --> 19:37.230
Chenying!

19:38.060 --> 19:38.900
Chenying!

19:41.870 --> 19:42.710
Chenying!

19:43.950 --> 19:44.790
Chenying!

19:45.780 --> 19:47.500
She is not your Xiaoxiao.

19:47.630 --> 19:50.300
She's fake.

19:51.020 --> 19:52.820
- She's fake.
- No.

19:52.820 --> 19:54.390
- She's fake!
- No.

19:54.580 --> 19:55.710
She's fake!

19:55.710 --> 19:56.550
Chenying.

19:56.710 --> 19:57.990
Chenying, save me!

19:58.430 --> 19:59.270
She wants to harm me.

19:59.500 --> 20:00.340
She wants to harm me!

20:00.580 --> 20:01.460
Who wants to harm you?

20:02.390 --> 20:03.260
Who wants to harm you?

20:03.780 --> 20:04.950
Xiaoxiao, don't be afraid.

20:05.540 --> 20:06.500
I will protect you.

20:42.780 --> 20:43.620
Chenying.

20:45.060 --> 20:45.900
Save me.

20:54.190 --> 20:55.030
You are awake.

21:00.470 --> 21:01.870
Remember what happened

21:02.740 --> 21:03.710
before you fell?

21:20.190 --> 21:21.030
From this day on,

21:21.470 --> 21:22.470
don't go out.

21:23.150 --> 21:24.150
Stay home and recover.

21:25.780 --> 21:26.620
Do you hear me?

21:37.100 --> 21:38.026
Greetings, Marshal Qin.

21:38.670 --> 21:40.020
I've thought

21:40.020 --> 21:41.670
about your plan
to attack Yunzhou and Luozhou.

21:42.150 --> 21:43.260
Yunzhou is not as strategic

21:43.430 --> 21:44.270
as Youzhou,

21:44.740 --> 21:45.780
but it has many plains,

21:45.990 --> 21:47.390
with open land and no cover.

21:47.820 --> 21:49.470
Reconnaissance would be very hard.

21:53.100 --> 21:54.500
We haven't set foot

21:54.500 --> 21:55.820
in the Guanhe River for 30 years.

21:56.150 --> 21:58.740
And we know little about Yunzhou.

21:59.020 --> 21:59.910
Attacking Yunzhou and Luozhou

22:00.340 --> 22:01.470
may not be the best move.

22:02.190 --> 22:03.260
If you have doubts,

22:03.950 --> 22:04.820
I'm willing to go

22:04.820 --> 22:05.780
and scout out Yunzhou.

22:06.820 --> 22:07.990
The scouts sent there before

22:07.990 --> 22:08.870
never returned.

22:09.190 --> 22:10.470
General Duan leads the army.

22:10.710 --> 22:11.740
How can he risk himself?

22:11.740 --> 22:13.020
I will not fail you.

22:18.300 --> 22:19.140
General Duan,

22:19.780 --> 22:20.740
think this through.

22:21.470 --> 22:22.540
The battle is imminent.

22:22.910 --> 22:24.060
The time you have left

22:24.870 --> 22:25.710
is running out.

22:27.430 --> 22:28.270
I'll finish the task

22:29.150 --> 22:30.060
within ten days.

22:30.540 --> 22:31.380
Good.

22:31.700 --> 22:33.380
(Liang)

22:38.060 --> 22:38.900
General,

22:39.390 --> 22:40.300
this is dangerous.

22:40.300 --> 22:41.140
Say no more.

22:41.710 --> 22:42.550
I know my limits.

22:43.430 --> 22:44.540
Go prepare with Han Lingqiu.

22:45.190 --> 22:46.030
You'll go with me.

22:47.190 --> 22:48.030
Yes.

23:02.670 --> 23:03.950
(Without the sense of touch,)

23:05.540 --> 23:06.580
(every movement I make)

23:07.260 --> 23:08.870
(relies on my body's momentum.)

23:08.870 --> 23:10.470
(Essence of Spring)

23:10.470 --> 23:11.410
(If I encounter danger)

23:12.020 --> 23:13.060
(in Yunzhou,)

23:14.230 --> 23:15.580
(with only this momentum,)

23:16.630 --> 23:18.020
(what are my chances of victory?)

23:24.710 --> 23:26.230
(I can't feel the instant I land)

23:29.190 --> 23:30.470
(nor the slightest shift)

23:31.390 --> 23:32.390
(in the air.)

23:48.260 --> 23:49.100
Dried fruits.

23:49.950 --> 23:50.950
Candied fruit.

23:52.870 --> 23:53.710
Mother.

23:54.190 --> 23:55.950
Mother, wait for me.

23:55.950 --> 23:57.500
(I wonder if hearing can replace touch.)

23:57.500 --> 23:58.340
Mother.

23:59.190 --> 24:00.300
(It seems not.)

24:01.060 --> 24:01.910
(The battlefield)

24:01.910 --> 24:02.910
(is far more complex.)

24:02.910 --> 24:04.190
Watch where you're going.

24:04.190 --> 24:05.670
(How am I supposed to judge)

24:05.670 --> 24:06.580
(what's happening?)

24:38.340 --> 24:39.180
Is this...

24:40.100 --> 24:40.940
raining?

25:31.190 --> 25:32.780
Sir, are you alright?

25:32.780 --> 25:33.670
I'm always so clumsy.

25:33.670 --> 25:34.510
I'm so sorry.

25:35.340 --> 25:36.870
Luckily, you're fine.

25:45.190 --> 25:46.060
(Without touch,)

25:47.540 --> 25:48.710
(my awareness is much weaker.)

26:33.300 --> 26:34.430
You like rainy days?

26:36.740 --> 26:37.820
I only just started to.

26:41.870 --> 26:42.710
Why?

26:45.020 --> 26:45.860
Look.

26:46.430 --> 26:48.260
At first, it's a fine, soft itch.

26:48.820 --> 26:50.780
Then it turns cool and moist.

26:51.630 --> 26:52.820
When it pours,

26:53.260 --> 26:54.670
it becomes a faint ache.

26:58.190 --> 26:59.470
I used to like rainy days too.

27:02.820 --> 27:04.480
I often carried out missions
in the rain.

27:05.820 --> 27:07.060
After that, whenever it rained,

27:08.430 --> 27:09.479
I'd think of the dampness

27:09.490 --> 27:11.990
and blood-tinged stench
hidden in the rain.

27:18.910 --> 27:20.390
But just now, I changed my mind.

27:22.820 --> 27:23.660
Rain

27:24.630 --> 27:25.630
is only rain.

27:28.230 --> 27:29.780
Rain didn't bring the evils

27:31.150 --> 27:32.340
hidden in it.

27:35.910 --> 27:36.990
You do recover easily

27:36.990 --> 27:38.300
after being hurt.

27:38.910 --> 27:40.540
So different from the dazed man

27:40.540 --> 27:41.910
in the rain just now.

27:46.740 --> 27:47.580
Simu,

27:49.630 --> 27:50.870
we must part for a while.

27:52.300 --> 27:53.190
I'm going to Yunzhou

27:53.540 --> 27:54.380
to scout.

27:56.670 --> 27:58.300
But without touch,

27:59.430 --> 28:00.580
you're almost an invalid.

28:01.150 --> 28:02.060
If danger finds you,

28:02.430 --> 28:03.820
you may not leave unscathed.

28:06.710 --> 28:07.740
You're worried about me?

28:11.430 --> 28:13.060
I only fear
you'll harm your five senses,

28:13.820 --> 28:15.300
or even lose your life,

28:15.870 --> 28:16.710
wouldn't my promise

28:16.710 --> 28:17.740
to you be for nothing?

28:33.020 --> 28:34.060
My father taught me

28:34.060 --> 28:35.150
how to sense touch

28:36.260 --> 28:37.340
by drawing on the wind.

28:38.630 --> 28:40.470
But mortals can't see the wind.

28:44.060 --> 28:45.430
You mean the wind

28:46.910 --> 28:48.190
like silken threads?

29:16.950 --> 29:18.230
Dust is extremely sensitive

29:18.230 --> 29:19.150
to subtle fluctuations.

29:20.540 --> 29:21.670
You can use it

29:22.230 --> 29:23.740
to sense the changes around you.

30:27.100 --> 30:28.150
Foxy,

30:29.300 --> 30:30.820
stay alive.

31:07.340 --> 31:08.180
Chenying,

31:09.990 --> 31:11.060
I haven't seen you

31:11.060 --> 31:12.260
with Miss He lately.

31:13.630 --> 31:15.190
You keep sighing.

31:17.910 --> 31:19.580
If you keep sighing like this,

31:20.300 --> 31:21.580
your Xiaoxiao

31:21.950 --> 31:23.300
won't be able to stand it.

31:29.870 --> 31:30.870
Lin,

31:31.950 --> 31:32.870
tell me.

31:33.710 --> 31:35.300
If another fake you

31:35.300 --> 31:36.580
appears,

31:36.990 --> 31:38.260
and I still can't tell,

31:38.740 --> 31:39.670
what should I do?

31:42.950 --> 31:45.230
Then look even more carefully.

31:46.020 --> 31:47.300
A fake is still a fake.

31:47.910 --> 31:49.100
He'll slip up.

31:50.150 --> 31:50.990
I believe

31:51.230 --> 31:52.340
that with your wit,

31:52.950 --> 31:54.260
you'll know how to tell.

32:13.150 --> 32:14.500
The new reform is

32:15.150 --> 32:16.150
not yet complete,

32:16.300 --> 32:17.540
and you're already leaving?

32:18.500 --> 32:20.430
The administrative framework
is taking shape.

32:20.910 --> 32:21.780
It can be carried out

32:21.780 --> 32:23.300
by the Vice Commissioner.

32:23.540 --> 32:24.820
I'm heading to Shunzhou

32:24.820 --> 32:26.020
to handle a few minor matters.

32:26.780 --> 32:28.740
Shunzhou's local powers run deep.

32:29.820 --> 32:31.020
What you are planning

32:31.390 --> 32:32.580
must be perilous.

32:33.580 --> 32:34.950
It may not go as you wish.

32:35.430 --> 32:36.950
No need for you to worry.

32:37.470 --> 32:38.430
General Duan,

32:38.430 --> 32:39.390
worry

32:39.390 --> 32:40.740
about your position instead.

32:41.500 --> 32:42.340
Yunzhou is dangerous.

32:42.910 --> 32:44.780
Aren't you afraid of no return?

32:47.260 --> 32:48.430
Rest easy.

32:48.740 --> 32:50.060
I'm looking forward to the game

32:50.060 --> 32:50.910
with you in Nandu.

32:52.100 --> 32:53.340
I'll return safe and sound.

32:54.820 --> 32:55.660
In that case,

32:56.670 --> 32:58.260
let's meet again in Nandu.

33:29.230 --> 33:30.340
Marshal Qin invites you

33:30.670 --> 33:31.656
to the Yamen.

33:50.540 --> 33:51.380
It's her.

33:51.820 --> 33:53.430
She's the one troubling Shuozhou.

33:56.430 --> 33:57.630
Marshal Qin summoned me here

33:58.470 --> 33:59.780
for something like this?

33:59.780 --> 34:00.620
How dare you?

34:00.870 --> 34:01.950
You brazen evil spirit,

34:01.950 --> 34:03.670
surrender at once!

34:03.670 --> 34:04.990
What a fraud!

34:05.190 --> 34:06.372
How dare you mislead the crowd

34:06.383 --> 34:07.230
before me?

34:08.660 --> 34:10.100
Captain Meng, that's not true.

34:10.950 --> 34:12.620
We invited her here

34:12.631 --> 34:14.303
(Clear-sighted and Astute)
based on proof.

34:14.470 --> 34:15.310
Indeed.

34:15.470 --> 34:16.430
If she aided

34:16.430 --> 34:18.020
General Duan with heretical arts

34:18.020 --> 34:19.140
and disrupted discipline,

34:19.390 --> 34:20.470
that is a grave offense.

34:20.470 --> 34:21.910
What proof do you have?

34:41.990 --> 34:43.500
It was her.

34:43.500 --> 34:44.540
She stole my identity.

34:45.990 --> 34:46.910
Don't be afraid.

34:47.620 --> 34:49.100
I'll back you up.

34:49.350 --> 34:50.190
Come on.

34:50.750 --> 34:51.750
Tell everyone here

34:51.950 --> 34:53.540
what happened.

34:57.750 --> 34:59.580
I'm the real He Xiaoxiao.

34:59.830 --> 35:00.910
This evil spirit

35:01.100 --> 35:02.220
took my post

35:02.470 --> 35:03.580
and tried to trap me.

35:05.430 --> 35:06.470
Luckily,

35:06.470 --> 35:08.020
Daoist Mingfeng saved me.

35:08.660 --> 35:11.060
Only then could I seek justice.

35:11.060 --> 35:11.910
Are you finished?

35:14.790 --> 35:16.620
You could find no fault

35:17.350 --> 35:18.540
with General Duan,

35:19.100 --> 35:20.020
so you smear him

35:20.020 --> 35:20.910
and those around him?

35:21.750 --> 35:22.590
That's right.

35:23.180 --> 35:24.540
It's just her story.

35:25.100 --> 35:26.350
You can't frame us so easily.

35:28.020 --> 35:29.620
Since you claim it's a frame-up,

35:29.950 --> 35:31.060
how do you explain

35:31.060 --> 35:32.350
there are two He Xiaoxiaos?

35:37.930 --> 35:40.310
I've spent decades vanquishing demons.

35:40.320 --> 35:41.510
What I do best

35:41.510 --> 35:44.520
is forcing evil spirits
to reveal their true form.

36:02.020 --> 36:02.860
Everyone, look!

36:03.430 --> 36:04.390
This...

36:04.390 --> 36:05.230
The evil spirit...

36:05.950 --> 36:07.350
It revealed its true form!

36:07.990 --> 36:08.910
An evil spirit!

36:09.060 --> 36:09.910
He Xiaoxiao,

36:10.580 --> 36:11.500
do you plead guilty?

36:13.100 --> 36:14.660
If you want to lock me up

36:15.580 --> 36:16.430
and investigate me,

36:17.350 --> 36:18.270
go ahead.

36:27.270 --> 36:28.990
You have less than a day left.

36:30.060 --> 36:30.900
Move fast.

36:34.450 --> 36:35.310
Take her.

36:35.310 --> 36:36.150
Yes.

36:36.790 --> 36:37.910
General Duan ordered me

36:37.910 --> 36:38.790
to protect Miss He.

36:39.620 --> 36:40.790
Who dares lay a hand on her?

36:42.620 --> 36:43.460
Meng,

36:45.310 --> 36:46.150
it is alright.

36:49.540 --> 36:50.380
Lead the way.

36:57.390 --> 36:58.470
Marshal!

37:16.180 --> 37:17.020
Lock it now.

37:21.140 --> 37:21.980
Hurry.

37:24.950 --> 37:25.790
Move, move.

37:28.180 --> 37:29.140
Go on. Move.

37:40.270 --> 37:42.180
I've come to the mortal world
many times,

37:43.310 --> 37:44.990
but prison is new.

37:48.470 --> 37:50.910
To hold this mortal body,

37:52.020 --> 37:53.660
these are less useful

37:56.100 --> 37:57.220
than wooden bars

37:57.220 --> 37:58.540
and iron chains.

38:23.180 --> 38:24.020
General,

38:25.830 --> 38:27.470
I had to suffer for trading five senses

38:30.100 --> 38:31.870
with you once.

38:56.620 --> 38:57.460
Miss He,

38:58.470 --> 38:59.430
what are you, truly?

39:00.990 --> 39:02.100
Don't tell me

39:02.606 --> 39:03.660
you never had your doubts.

39:05.790 --> 39:07.140
So, you really are...

39:10.100 --> 39:11.700
I'm the spirit you speak of.

39:22.950 --> 39:24.270
I will distract the guards.

39:24.700 --> 39:25.660
You must leave at once.

39:30.390 --> 39:31.580
Don't you dislike me?

39:31.750 --> 39:32.870
Go as I tell you.

39:34.830 --> 39:35.830
You helped Xu and us

39:36.470 --> 39:37.620
against North Chong.

39:38.620 --> 39:39.700
I don't care what you are.

39:40.540 --> 39:41.750
I'm not an ingrate.

40:02.270 --> 40:03.350
Since I came out of prison,

40:03.350 --> 40:04.950
you've followed us all the way here.

40:05.830 --> 40:07.020
Why not make your move?

40:17.660 --> 40:19.020
Did you think a few dirty tricks

40:19.430 --> 40:20.990
would be enough to deal with me?

40:21.750 --> 40:22.590
True.

40:22.790 --> 40:25.220
We can't handle you.

40:25.470 --> 40:26.430
But...

40:28.700 --> 40:30.790
he can.

40:34.500 --> 40:35.470
They said

40:36.270 --> 40:37.910
you're not the real Xiaoxiao.

40:38.700 --> 40:40.270
They lied to me, didn't they?

40:45.500 --> 40:47.660
There was never any He Xiaoxiao.

40:49.140 --> 40:50.700
There is only me, a spirit.

40:52.100 --> 40:53.660
Chenying, look.

40:53.660 --> 40:54.580
Did you hear?

40:54.830 --> 40:56.060
She admitted it herself.

40:56.390 --> 40:57.660
She is that spirit.

40:59.870 --> 41:00.750
I am

41:00.750 --> 41:02.140
your real Xiaoxiao.

41:02.750 --> 41:03.590
Chenying,

41:03.750 --> 41:04.870
help me get

41:04.870 --> 41:05.710
that jade pendant.

41:05.720 --> 41:06.620
That belongs to me.

41:08.220 --> 41:09.060
All right?

41:11.350 --> 41:12.200
So, your aim

41:12.200 --> 41:13.620
was the Spirits Lantern after all.

41:15.700 --> 41:16.620
Chenying,

41:17.180 --> 41:18.390
go now.

41:19.020 --> 41:20.620
Help me bring that thing over.

41:21.990 --> 41:23.060
Otherwise,

41:24.390 --> 41:25.750
I will cast you aside.

41:28.350 --> 41:29.190
Go.

41:44.390 --> 41:45.230
Hurry.

42:14.700 --> 42:15.660
Boy,

42:15.660 --> 42:16.500
this is your moment.

42:21.950 --> 42:22.790
Child,

42:23.180 --> 42:24.146
I'll give you a chance.

42:24.700 --> 42:25.580
Pick up that knife.

42:25.870 --> 42:27.100
Kill this malevolent spirit.

42:35.870 --> 42:36.830
After he kills her,

42:37.180 --> 42:38.020
you must give me

42:38.077 --> 42:39.146
the wealth as you promised.

42:39.500 --> 42:40.990
Yes. Pick it up.

42:40.990 --> 42:41.830
Pick it up.

42:43.220 --> 42:44.620
She killed your father.

42:45.180 --> 42:46.660
She's the one who killed him.

42:46.950 --> 42:48.580
Don't you want revenge for him?

42:55.060 --> 42:55.900
But...

42:56.910 --> 42:59.020
My father was killed
by the Chong people.

42:59.310 --> 43:00.150
Not by her.

43:02.270 --> 43:04.350
She consumed your father's obsession.

43:04.870 --> 43:06.220
If your father still had

43:06.220 --> 43:07.060
an obsession,

43:07.220 --> 43:08.750
he would not have died so soon.

43:09.950 --> 43:10.790
Quick.

43:10.990 --> 43:11.870
Kill her.

43:11.870 --> 43:12.870
- Quick.
- Quick.

43:12.870 --> 43:13.830
Quick.

43:13.830 --> 43:14.910
- Kill her.
- Quick.

43:14.910 --> 43:15.750
Hurry and kill her.

43:21.100 --> 43:22.220
- Quick.
- Quick.

43:22.220 --> 43:23.620
Quick. Kill her.

43:23.620 --> 43:24.460
Quick.

43:24.910 --> 43:25.750
Kill her now.

43:26.020 --> 43:26.870
Kill her.

43:28.310 --> 43:29.580
Didn't you want to fight?

43:30.350 --> 43:32.020
Kill her, and you can go fight.

43:32.470 --> 43:33.310
Quick.

43:34.310 --> 43:35.580
Kill her. Kill her.

43:40.801 --> 43:46.131
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:46.461 --> 43:50.711
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:52.071 --> 43:57.441
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:57.741 --> 44:02.341
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:03.431 --> 44:05.271
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:17.481 --> 44:22.921
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:23.101 --> 44:27.431
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:28.801 --> 44:34.191
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:34.421 --> 44:38.361
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:40.131 --> 44:42.021
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:44.681 --> 44:47.841
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:47.841 --> 44:50.371
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:50.371 --> 44:55.891
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:55.891 --> 44:59.131
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:59.131 --> 45:03.991
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

45:04.331 --> 45:07.351
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

45:07.351 --> 45:10.171
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

45:10.431 --> 45:12.961
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

45:12.961 --> 45:18.381
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

45:18.551 --> 45:21.621
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

45:21.781 --> 45:26.681
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

45:26.891 --> 45:30.361
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
